These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, french, canadian
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, dressmaker, videographer, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, taxi
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 6. the videographer is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
 8. the project-manager is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the person driving the taxi is the videographer##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the canadian##1
11. the french is on the left or right of the electrician##3
12. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the chinese##5
13. the videographer is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
14. the chinese is the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the chinese is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality         | brazilian     | chinese   | canadian | french |
| Job   | dressmaker | project-manager   | electrician   | videographer  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Transport     | airplane    | motorbike | jet-ski     | taxi    |

