.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, blend, swisher, chaman
House: modern, craftsman, cottage, gothic-revival
 1. the swisher-smoker is between the modern house and the blend-smoker##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the craftsman house##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
 5. the modern house is not to the left of the blend-smoker##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
 8. the cottage house is in an odd position##4
 9. the old-henry-smoker is the craftsman house##1
10. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the modern house##3
11. the modern house is not to the left of the swisher-smoker##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the blend-smoker##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the craftsman house##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Cigar   | blend    | swisher  | chaman | old-henry |
| House           | cottage | gothic-revival | modern    | craftsman  |

