.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving, sudoku
4 different pets are kept: fish, rat, ferret, turtle
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, rose, poppy, daffodil
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who growsorchid##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8
 7. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person who growsrose##8
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku   | skydiving | card-games |
| Pet   | fish     | ferret  | turtle   | rat      |
| Flower   | rose | orchid    | poppy      | daffodil       |
| Sport         | sailing    | climbing | surfing   | cycling    |

