 3. the fan of indie is the musician##1
 4. the fan of folk is between the dancer and the electrician##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the software-developer##1
10. the electrician is the pall-mall-smoker##1
11. the dunhill-smoker is not to the right of the fan of jazz##8
12. the dancer is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the electrician is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

