 1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the fan of pop##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is the nigerian##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the dutch##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the thai##6
 8. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of punk##1
12. the fan of dubstep is not the argentine##6
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
