 6. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking milk##7
 7. the person playing canasta is not to the left of the person playing monopoly##8
 8. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is golf##7
 9. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
10. the librarian is not to the left of the librarian##8
11. the electrician is on the far left##1
12. the videographer is on the far right##1
13. the person playing canasta is the person who's sport is skiing##1
14. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
15. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
