.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, whist, billiard, chess
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, swisher, havana, vegafina
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the person playing billiard is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
 7. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person playing whist is not to the right of the swisher-smoker##8
11. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Game      | monopoly   | chess     | billiard    | whist |
| Cigar   | prince  | vegafina      | havana     | swisher     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

