 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the person playing go is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
