 9. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
12. the person eating plum is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person playing billiard##8

