 7. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the photographer##8
 9. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the british##3
10. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the project-manager##7
11. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

